tform we moved over to VRBO and it has been a great experience so far. <\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/trustedhousesitters\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">TrustedHouseSitters<\/a><br>If you love animals, TrustedHouseSitters is a great option! These are people allowing you to live in their house for free if you can look after their pet or watering the plants while they are away.<br><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\">\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-travel-insurance\">Travel Insurance<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/travel-insurance\/\">Travel insurance<\/a> is one of the first things we check when traveling, especially when planning an expensive trip or when traveling with a lot of gear like cameras and laptops we make sure our insurance is adjusted to our situation. You can relax and travel stress-free for a few dollars per day! (Read our guide to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/travel-insurance\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">the best travel insurances)<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/heymondo-travel-insurance\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Heymondo<\/a><br>We have been a long-time Heymondo user with a Annual Multitrip insurance. We have used our policies mostly for medical coverage in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/thailand\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Thailand<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Costa Rica<\/a>. Thailand was cheap but Costa Rica very(!) expensive so I was happy to have the insurance. On top of that we also had damage on electronic equipment.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/nomad-travel-insurance\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">SafetyWing<\/a><br>It is a flexible travel insurance for nomads by nomads. Compare both insurances and find out what suits you best.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\">\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"finding-cheap-flights\">Finding cheap flights<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Saving on the price of a flight ticket is a massive budget-saver. There are quite a few tricks to find the cheapest flight tickets, but it starts with research.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/skyscanner\/\">Skyscanner<\/a><br>This is our go-to tool when it comes to booking a flight. It is a flight comparison tool with  very useful tools of the price of a flight per day.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/flights.google.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Google Flights<\/a><br>This tool from Google is ideal for tracking flight prices and getting to know if the current price is a great deal or too expensive. Additionally their map tool is useful when you&#x2019;re looking to fly &#x2018;anywhere&#x2019; from your current destination. <\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\">\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"finding-cheap-flights\">Transportation<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When it comes to getting around a destination we either travel by rental car, bus or train. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">SunnyCars (Rental Cars)<\/a> <br>We prefer to be well-insured (because we&#x2019;ve experienced a scam or two). Sunnycars has all insurances included in the price, so no hidden fees when collecting your car.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transportation\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">12Go (Public transport)<\/a> <br>Whether you need a train, bus or private shuttle. 12Go is the first place we look because they offer a bit of everything at many destinations around the world.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\">\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"purchasing-a-visa\">Purchasing a visa <\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Applying for a visa might be necessary when you travel to a new destination. Check on <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/get-visa\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iVisa<\/a> if you need a visa for your next travel destination. They provide a service to directly order your visa and have it all ready within a certain amount of time without any hassle.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/get-visa\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Go to iVisa and check your visa requirements<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/bali\/visa-bali-indonesia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Bali, Indonesia visa requirements<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/visa-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka visa requirements<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/egypt\/egypt-visa\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Egypt visa requirements<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Travel Resources Below are the travel companies we use for all of our trips. When you purchase something through some of these links we get a little kickback but you pay the same, win-win! Accommodation Lovely and cozy accommodations are one of the first things we look at when planning our trips. We love being [&hellip;]","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_relevanssi_hide_post":"","_relevanssi_pin_for_all":"","_relevanssi_pin_keywords":"","_relevanssi_unpin_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_include_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_exclude_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_no_append":"","_relevanssi_related_not_related":"","_relevanssi_related_posts":"63919,5404,9330,3933,11868,13588"},"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yo